Reverse SPF (Sender Policy Framework)
=====================================

This script will generate a set if IPv4 CIDR blocks listed in the SPF
records of a list of domains.  (RFC 4408)

Usage:

  spf.py domain-1.com domain-2.com ...

Requires
--------

Python 2.x  (may work with 3, didn't test)
dnspython   (www.dnspython.org)

